{"tid":380822,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[晚餐post] 蒸水蛋","createTime":"2017-08-30T12:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T06:55:07.000Z","uid":123204,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc2ed5b5a7820229ee3237a62fc5b0c08d134e30","tid":380822,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dph70ye5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdph70ye5&h=987812f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話說每日做完嘢已經好累<br />\n簡單蒸個水蛋就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本上一星期都整兩三晚<br />\n今晚試落金華火腿雞湯 本身聞下個湯後都驚太重口味未必carry 到<br />\n點知食落都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過後段用細火蒸 搞到成 4 5 個字先成型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲葱擺到乾曬又係敗筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9ec931bb714c3387d4dcffd29ddd85bca423c8","tid":380822,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:04:42.000Z","msg":"好清"},{"pid":"9fc1e62713cae0b4bb91cab0aeae45f7fe647419","tid":380822,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:07:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好清</blockquote><br />\n因為落雞湯本身已經夠味 唔洗再加豉油嗰啲"},{"pid":"bfbbc47f741fe931ef67da0da0b0cff569e8c874","tid":380822,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:18:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好清</blockquote><br />\n贊gargar"},{"pid":"9aa4ea68c10a058e63fd247761edad0a182f0598","tid":380822,"uid":6562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:45:16.000Z","msg":"好滑咁"},{"pid":"9cfe941358801c0f770a29e63178dc8ffc803623","tid":380822,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T14:08:17.000Z","msg":"有功架，蒸得幾靚仔"},{"pid":"859da2a318eb132924543ef9a27f66a058b8f717","tid":380822,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T14:17:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有功架，蒸得幾靚仔</blockquote><br />\n成日蒸 所以叫做熟手啲"},{"pid":"8abaa20a5eeae6e1cacf18fbd222e5558e5e72a1","tid":380822,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:01:04.000Z","msg":"清雞好食過金華火腿"},{"pid":"806e438d3e42c7938b59af36041f9a4ac20c25d6","tid":380822,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:02:09.000Z","msg":"史雲生細盒加兩隻蛋 大火蒸10分鐘 100%成功超滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3eb8a242f51911ac77a57a9d2fe3614e2cc40a0","tid":380822,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:06:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>清雞好食過金華火腿</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上次瑤柱都正"},{"pid":"0948f121bf07769c02998b912502acf54239d440","tid":380822,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:07:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>史雲生細盒加兩隻蛋 大火蒸10分鐘 100%成功超滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加雞湯其中一個好處係無咩泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我跟人頭落蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8047dc52a8adfcc4549961c094a4d5fc8455011b","tid":380822,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:08:41.000Z","msg":"倒咗佢喇~ 有甲由呀~~~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b7c1052fdee9e06538818be387e7f760151e19","tid":380822,"uid":138382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:40:14.000Z","msg":"勁中意食蒸水蛋 下次試下落雞湯先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf45a567b874a125714473386e7029872225624","tid":380822,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:40:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>倒咗佢喇~ 有甲由呀~~~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食曬啦 應該ok嘅<br />\n屋企都好多年無見佢地<br />\n講開出街食都硬係覺得會污糟啲"},{"pid":"cce94eaecc58c0888fbd05cb742a2b1f5e65b58b","tid":380822,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:53:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>勁中意食蒸水蛋 下次試下落雞湯先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔錯架<br />\n有時再清淡啲就落水同麻油"},{"pid":"ff9964c35f8db49f5f19fd2db61438c31c141822","tid":380822,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T01:58:38.000Z","msg":"今晚又想整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4192097a3d188c11ee8b4f7d64711e12bccc1adf","tid":380822,"uid":65656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:34:17.000Z","msg":"講黎聽下你點整<br />\n如果用水+麻油既方法<br />\n我次次整都整到好多氣港好失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854bef4929fc4da30cd669efd1d93f5a4ff94208","tid":380822,"uid":123204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:41:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講黎聽下你點整<br />\n如果用水+麻油既方法<br />\n我次次整都整到好多氣港好失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多氣泡係指overcook, 無畢泡定倒汗水？<br />\n其實一樣<br />\n跟人頭落蛋<br />\n大約蛋水一比一多少少<br />\n用熟水 未試過生水講唔到分別<br />\n想滑啲就落多啲水 但耐熟啲 <br />\n再撈啲麻油<br />\n臨蒸就清泡 我自己就用火槍燒 如果無火槍用匙羹畢都ok<br />\n用蒸爐就無倒汗水 用煲就可以包錫紙<br />\n<br />\n至於蒸幾耐就好睇情況<br />\n我連埋其他野蒸就15分鐘 就咁蒸十分鐘到都ok<br />\n器材 環境 用料都唔同 真係要慢慢試出黎"},{"pid":"9103ee5a7d15da136e6a4a173611d87e6d153e9f","tid":380822,"uid":93629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:48:35.000Z","msg":"用個煲蓋/保鮮紙/錫紙 乜都好蓋住蒸<br />\n葱就唔會變黑"},{"pid":"cbd5a7d066852ca6d4d680534b9d47309df8bd82","tid":380822,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:00:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用個煲蓋/保鮮紙/錫紙 乜都好蓋住蒸<br />\n葱就唔會變黑</blockquote><br />\n我係蒸完先落 純粹為好睇啲<br />\n菜檔成日唔送葱 搞到擺乾曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e89a05f4ca234baa5c5aa8dc415cede92fbacb0","tid":380822,"uid":53885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:06:57.000Z","msg":"有泡/打唔散既蛋白可以用sau gay隔一隔 蒸出黎就靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c2bccca39f176366e3bfb3384cb6acb28ac99b","tid":380822,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:09:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有泡/打唔散既蛋白可以用sau gay隔一隔 蒸出黎就靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n怕洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過星六日都可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f97c8b314419b76d328bc96cdd9e648f8cb6d2e","tid":380822,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:30:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有泡/打唔散既蛋白可以用sau gay隔一隔 蒸出黎就靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n怕洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過星六日都可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即洗幾秒鐘，你唔即洗要洗得耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3109e31280db8e892e75766bdf1bb5e0ec138b4","tid":380822,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:42:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有泡/打唔散既蛋白可以用sau gay隔一隔 蒸出黎就靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n怕洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過星六日都可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即洗幾秒鐘，你唔即洗要洗得耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾秒就咁用水沖？？<br />\n唔落皂唔自在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0ea2bdab1e000056b01030ef592ac75d81ea75","tid":380822,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:52:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有泡/打唔散既蛋白可以用sau gay隔一隔 蒸出黎就靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n怕洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過星六日都可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即洗幾秒鐘，你唔即洗要洗得耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾秒就咁用水沖？？<br />\n唔落皂唔自在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實無油既野用水洗啦，用皂最尾又係食返啲皂落肚"}]}